<title>USA: Eltrax Systems acquires modem maker.</title>
<headline>Eltrax Systems acquires modem maker.</headline>
<dateline>MINNETONKA, Minn. 1997-02-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Eltrax Systems Inc said Monday it completed the purchase of the business and certain assets of the MST division of MRK Technologies Ltd of Cleveland, Ohio, for about $2 million.</p>
<p>Data Communications company Eltrax said hardware maker MST disclosed that it had revenue of about $9 million for 1996, with earnings before general and administrative expenses of aobut $1 million.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk 312 408 8787))</p>
